{"tid":646379,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中超隊以全球最高薪誘雲加","createTime":"2018-04-29T03:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T04:33:34.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6dfc61fbcb9ef4a4ecc83542d07eebc7d92acd30","tid":646379,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"雲加宣佈季後離開阿仙奴後，下個目的地眾說紛紜，最近有指中超球隊開出全球最高教練人工利誘他加盟。<br />\n根據英國《鏡報》報道，雲加（Arsene Wenger）在宣佈即將離開執教了22年的阿仙奴後，已收到多份聘書，當中以來自中超的球會出手最為豪氣，要是這名68歲老帥首肯，將會成為全球最高薪教練。<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">意大利名帥納比執教中國國家隊，年薪為2400萬鎊，而雲加入主中超球隊後，人工會更高</span>，而他<span style=\"color: red;\">現時於阿仙奴每年只賺800萬鎊</span>；至於英超最高薪領隊為曼城的哥迪奧拿，1年人工有1600萬鎊。<br />\n不過，據知雲加屬意執教法國或西班牙球會，相信以巴黎聖日耳門的機會最高，因為他們財力雄厚之餘，主帥艾美利剛在周五宣佈將於球季結束後離任。"},{"pid":"660edbf7d0c588890c1777e285ff00570a5a0d30","tid":646379,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"714c7c3aed884358656418e238144b1be3b80750","tid":646379,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"法國國家隊"},{"pid":"f2b77e79029eb20c01375c04c707aedc89c717dc","tid":646379,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"電叻教中超，我轉捧個隊支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00233dfaebff387f5c8f0f38f08bd60270c2517e","tid":646379,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"660edbf7d0c588890c1777e285ff00570a5a0d30","tid":646379,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas